# Custom Theme System Implementation Plan for T3 Code

## Overview

This plan replaces the existing `"light" | "dark" | "system"` toggle with a proper multi-theme system. Three named themes ship at launch. The `resolvedTheme: "light" | "dark"` surface is preserved so all four Shiki/diff consumers continue working without changes.

