# Custom Theme System — T3 Code

## Context

The app currently has a minimal light/dark/system toggle in `apps/web/src/hooks/useTheme.ts` using `useSyncExternalStore`. This plan replaces it with a proper named-theme system: three built-in themes (`t3-dark`, `t3-light`, `t3-midnight`) covering all existing CSS variables plus new domain-specific ones (sidebar, editor, terminal, status bar). The `resolvedTheme: "light" | "dark"` surface is preserved so the four Shiki/diff consumers require zero changes.

---

## Files to Create

1. `packages/shared/src/theme.ts`
2. `apps/web/src/components/ThemeProvider.tsx`
3. `apps/web/src/components/ThemeSelector.tsx`

